      <h1>Complete Bakery Equipment List for Every Budget 2026</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span>📅 Updated: March 2026</span>
        <span>⏱️ 14 min read</span>
        <span>🇮🇳 India-focused pricing</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p><strong>What equipment does a bakery need? The complete bakery equipment list depends on what you bake, your production volume, and your budget.</strong> A home baker needs different equipment from an industrial bread factory. This guide breaks down the complete bakery equipment list by budget level — from a ₹50,000 home baker setup to a ₹50 lakh commercial bakery — with real prices from Indian suppliers in 2026.</p>

    <h2>The Complete Bakery Equipment List: Master Checklist</h2>
    <p>Here's every category of equipment a bakery might need. You won't need everything on this list — what you need depends on your menu and scale.</p>

    <h3>Ovens</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Convection oven (4–20 trays)</li>
      <li>Deck oven (1–4 decks)</li>
      <li>Rotary rack oven</li>
      <li>Pizza oven (if applicable)</li>
      <li>Microwave (for thawing, reheating)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Mixers & Processing</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Planetary mixer (5–60 litres)</li>
      <li>Spiral dough mixer (10–100 litres)</li>
      <li>Dough sheeter / laminator</li>
      <li>Bread divider and rounder</li>
      <li>Food processor / vegetable cutter</li>
      <li>Blender / food mill</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Refrigeration</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Commercial refrigerator (reach-in)</li>
      <li>Commercial freezer</li>
      <li>Blast chiller (for bake-off operations)</li>
      <li>Display refrigerator / cake counter</li>
      <li>Walk-in cold room (for larger operations)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Baking Tools & Smallwares</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Baking trays / sheet pans (30–100+ pieces)</li>
      <li>Bread tins / loaf pans</li>
      <li>Cake moulds and rings</li>
      <li>Muffin trays</li>
      <li>Silicone mats</li>
      <li>Piping bags and nozzles</li>
      <li>Palette knives and spatulas</li>
      <li>Bench scrapers</li>
      <li>Rolling pins</li>
      <li>Proofing baskets (bannetons)</li>
      <li>Pastry brushes</li>
      <li>Cake turntable</li>
      <li>Dough cutter / divider</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Weighing & Measuring</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Commercial digital scale (5–15 kg)</li>
      <li>Precision scale (0–3 kg, 0.1g accuracy)</li>
      <li>Measuring jugs and spoons</li>
      <li>Digital probe thermometer</li>
      <li>Oven thermometer</li>
      <li>Refrigerator thermometer</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Storage & Organisation</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Stainless steel work tables</li>
      <li>Shelving units</li>
      <li>Ingredient bins (flour, sugar)</li>
      <li>Proofing cabinet (for artisan bakers)</li>
      <li>Bread slicer (if selling sliced bread)</li>
      <li>Tray racks / bread racks</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Packaging & Display</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Bakery display counter / cabinet</li>
      <li>Point of sale counter</li>
      <li>Bread bags, cake boxes, packaging materials</li>
      <li>Label printer</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Cleaning & Sanitation</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Sink(s) — prep sink and handwash sink</li>
      <li>Dishwasher or dishwashing setup</li>
      <li>Food-safe cleaning materials and sanitisers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Bakery Equipment List by Budget</h2>

    <h3>Budget Level 1: Home Bakery Starter Kit (₹30,000 – ₹80,000)</h3>
    <p>For home bakers just starting to sell commercially. Limited production capacity but enough to test the market and build a customer base before investing more.</p>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Equipment</th><th>Price Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>OTG or small convection oven (4 tray)</td><td>₹8,000 – ₹25,000</td><td>Semi-commercial</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stand mixer (5–7 litre)</td><td>₹15,000 – ₹35,000</td><td>Entry-level commercial</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Baking trays (10 pieces)</td><td>₹2,000 – ₹5,000</td><td>Commercial grade</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Basic cake moulds and tins</td><td>₹2,000 – ₹4,000</td><td>–</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Digital scale</td><td>₹1,500 – ₹3,000</td><td>–</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Basic decorating tools</td><td>₹1,500 – ₹3,000</td><td>–</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>₹30,000 – ₹75,000</strong></td><td>–</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Budget Level 2: Small Commercial Bakery (₹3 lakh – ₹8 lakh)</h3>
    <p>For a dedicated commercial bakery with a small retail counter or delivery operation. Can produce 100–300 items per day depending on products.</p>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Equipment</th><th>Price Range</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>8-tray convection oven</td><td>₹90,000 – ₹1,50,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2-deck oven (for bread)</td><td>₹1,20,000 – ₹2,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>10-litre planetary mixer</td><td>₹45,000 – ₹80,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Single-door commercial fridge</td><td>₹25,000 – ₹50,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bakery display counter (small)</td><td>₹35,000 – ₹70,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Baking trays (30 pieces)</td><td>₹5,000 – ₹12,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stainless steel work table</td><td>₹8,000 – ₹18,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Tools, scales, thermometers</td><td>₹10,000 – ₹20,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>₹3,38,000 – ₹7,00,000</strong></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Budget Level 3: Medium Commercial Bakery (₹8 lakh – ₹20 lakh)</h3>
    <p>A well-equipped commercial bakery capable of producing 500–2,000 items daily. Can supply retail shops, cafés, and restaurants in addition to direct retail.</p>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Equipment</th><th>Price Range</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>10-tray convection oven (premium brand)</td><td>₹1,80,000 – ₹3,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3-deck oven with steam injection</td><td>₹2,80,000 – ₹5,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>20-litre planetary mixer</td><td>₹80,000 – ₹1,40,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>30-litre spiral mixer</td><td>₹90,000 – ₹1,60,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Double-door commercial fridge</td><td>₹60,000 – ₹1,20,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Commercial freezer</td><td>₹35,000 – ₹70,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bakery display counter (full)</td><td>₹80,000 – ₹1,80,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Dough sheeter</td><td>₹60,000 – ₹1,20,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Stainless steel tables & shelving</td><td>₹40,000 – ₹80,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Baking trays & tools (complete)</td><td>₹30,000 – ₹60,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>₹8,83,000 – ₹20,30,000</strong></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Budget Level 4: Large Commercial Bakery (₹25 lakh – ₹60 lakh+)</h3>
    <p>Industrial-scale production with rotary rack ovens, large-capacity mixers, and a walk-in cold room. Capable of producing thousands of items per day for wholesale distribution.</p>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Equipment</th><th>Price Range</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Full-rack rotary oven (2 units)</td><td>₹16,00,000 – ₹30,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>60-litre spiral mixer</td><td>₹2,00,000 – ₹4,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>40-litre planetary mixer</td><td>₹1,60,000 – ₹3,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Dough sheeter (heavy-duty)</td><td>₹1,20,000 – ₹2,50,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Walk-in cold room</td><td>₹3,00,000 – ₹6,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Blast chiller (10-tray)</td><td>₹2,00,000 – ₹4,50,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Display and retail refrigeration</td><td>₹2,00,000 – ₹4,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bread slicer (commercial)</td><td>₹80,000 – ₹2,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Tray racks, tables, shelving</td><td>₹2,00,000 – ₹4,00,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Packaging equipment</td><td>₹1,00,000 – ₹2,50,000</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>₹31,60,000 – ₹62,50,000</strong></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

